==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dictamnus
<hw>Dic*tam"nus</hw> <pr>(d⟦icr⟧k*t⟦acr⟧m"n⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. See <er>Dittany</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A suffrutescent herb, <spn>Dictamnus Fraxinella</spn> (the only
species), with strong perfume and showy flowers. The volatile oil of the
leaves is highly inflammable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dictaphone</ent>⟦br⟧
